<br>
Just because something makes it easier for you to level, that does not mean it's better.  It might be better for gaining levels/AAxp more quickly, but is it truly better for having fun?  Having fun, after all, is what this game is all about.  If all you want is to level as quickly as possible, you are missing the whole point.  Everquest has become a chore and you have yet to realize it.  I play it to have fun.  Nukes with larger amounts of damage and lower DPM ratios are fun.  I'd like to see them put more of these into the game, post level 50.  They are an easy way to add more fun to the game without adding more power to the class and upsetting the balance.<br>
<br>
-Raystonn<br>
